Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:05.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,360)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.44,0:01:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, young lady
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a fox
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:19.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(868,354)}调料区
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.70,0:01:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要归我了  可爱的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all mine, you sweet Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,启动发射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Initiating launch sequence
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望这次别又射偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope I don't miss again
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重聚的感觉真美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reunited, and it's going to feel so good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:06.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,718)}蟹老板
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet wampum
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.03,0:02:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.32,0:02:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用你的额头保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shield me with your forehead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.85,0:02:21.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是竞争对手痞老板又没偷到蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it was just another failed Krabby Patty theft attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:21.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by my arch-competitor, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我原先差点还把你当成威胁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For a second there, I mistook you for a threat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而你就只是个肮脏的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you're just a dirty, little man
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.29,0:02:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  小虾米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:41.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412,750)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.49,0:02:48.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来今天又失败了  对吧亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:48.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, typical day of failure, I see, huh, darling?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别说了  电脑老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it, computer wife
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就看不出来我累坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm exhausted?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不去做点有用的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go make yourself useful
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我合成点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and synthesize me up some grub?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看有什么吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we got here?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodie
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是全息肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holographic meatloaf again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么时候才能吃得到真正的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When am I going to get some real food?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板就吃得到真正的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs gets to eat real food
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at his daughter
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,块头跟鲸鱼一样大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's as big as a whale
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我能跟蟹老板一样成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:19.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be successful like Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.43,0:03:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我可以用某种办法跟他交换身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I could somehow just switch lives with him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道他的大号生活是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just to know what it's like
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那要不然你就来用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you just use
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.03,0:03:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个身份交换了解生活之变身机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Switch-Lives-Just-to-Know-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What-It's-Like-O-Mogrifier thing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上周二做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you built last Tuesday?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a brilliant idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你爸妈先前肯定就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your parents must have been, like
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半台电脑什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,part computer or something
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然很不愿意与你分离  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I hate to leave you, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要知道俗话说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you know what they say
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换身份  来去无牵挂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"a rolling stone gathers no algae"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear Neptune above
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened last night?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,640)}痞老板
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Mr. Plankton"?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who the davey?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在蟹堡王里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表示身份交换机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that means the life switcher
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was a success
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公司休闲装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Corporate casual
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个豪华蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two deluxe Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个豪华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two deluxe
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, there, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.88,0:05:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得拿个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need to take one of these patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回我办公室去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back to my office for, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进行抽查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bun inspection
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉不可以  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you can't do that, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为那个蟹黄堡是给客人吃的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because that patty is for the customer, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The customer?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把客人放热油里煮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll boil the customer in hot oil
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后再扒了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll rip out his
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  当然好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, yes, of course
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顾客至上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the lovely customer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你可以拿这俩蟹黄堡  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you can take these patties, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做出来是为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made them on the off chance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你今天可能决定要做抽查做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you decided to instigate some bun inspection today
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Plankton, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very nice
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.10,0:05:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All mine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's finally all mine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The patties
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,财富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the wealth
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏名声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the notoriety
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,504)}商务奖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,368)}金钱杂志
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.12,0:05:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.05,0:05:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是  又到星期二了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just that it's Tuesday again, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我能不能有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I was wondering if I could have my
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每周绩效评价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,weekly performance review
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,评价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Review?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please, sir, please
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我以前啥都没评价过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I've never reviewed anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了我表亲发给我的外国健身视频
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except for those foreign exercise videos
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my cousin sent me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托了  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想让你高兴又骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to make you so happy and proud
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现还行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing fine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开  让我自个儿做事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now leave me to my work
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是都把你打发走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I sent you away, Cretan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定有哪个方面需要改进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's got to be something I need to improve on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  酱料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, the sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.50,0:06:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.27,0:06:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酱料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sauce, I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放太多酱料了  总行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're using too much sauce, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,评完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Review's over
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.00,0:06:47.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:47.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是说酱料有点多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I said was a little too much sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal, really
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要我给你什么  升职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me, a promotion?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pro
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.40,0:07:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,升
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a promot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,升职
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a promotion?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, kid, you're, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在去当收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're on register now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Register?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glad that's over
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你还记不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, do you remember
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们先前怎么讨论私人空间问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that little talk we had about personal space?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.95,0:07:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有授权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm official
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.77,0:07:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,410)}联合收银员
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,联合收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Co-cashier?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个是不是已经认识很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, have you two known each other long?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能这么对待我  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't do this to me, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你真觉得我能一整天站外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm going to stand out there all day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,listening to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你脑子肯定进珊瑚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you must have coral wedged in your frontal lobe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你想要我干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.57,0:07:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要我的眼前能少一点黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like my view to be a little less yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you know what I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你喜欢灰色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hope you like gray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我能从这扇小窗户看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, I can see you through this little window
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再来打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, no more intrusions
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要开始写我成功故事的回忆录了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to begin writing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the memoirs of my success story
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家就乖乖待在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So everyone just stay the
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要什么就跟你爸直说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just tell Daddy what you want
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他非常忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's very busy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I please have a, um
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提前要一点零花钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an advance on my allowance?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能把你打发走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If it'll get you out of my antennae
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去嗨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hate me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得这好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think this is funny?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒是有那么几分好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In a cosmic sort of way, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  好笑先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Funny Man
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的病态乐趣是这么来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is this how you get your sick kicks?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不就是个普通的蟹黄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just an ordinary Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really did
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有客人点了中杯汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A customer ordered a medium soda
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我却给了大杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I gave him a large
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我却给了大杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gave him a large
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.08,0:09:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我玷污了蟹堡王的好名声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've soiled the good Krusty Krab name
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.27,0:09:25.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soiled it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我命令你住口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I command you to stop that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住口  回到你的工作岗位上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop that, and return to your post
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soiled it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西要按哪里才关得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the off button on this thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经决定好离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've decided I'm going to run away
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出走去认个新爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run away and find a new daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  触发了什么秘密关键词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, did I say the secret word?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's back?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驻守阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man your stations
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,红色警报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Red alert
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take cover
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲啥要掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take cover from what?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就在这附近某处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's around here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.77,0:10:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he goes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.14,0:10:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.21,0:10:03.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁来跟我说明下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.45,0:10:10.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,据说他是从最深的海沟爬出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some say he crawled out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the lowest trench in the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是水手当中最为粗俗的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's the saltiest of all of the sea dogs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是裤头村的头号公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's the most hated creature in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.31,0:10:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他最终还是得到了蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And he's finally got a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the barnacle is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是你的死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's your arch-competitor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.71,0:10:27.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:27.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一生中的目标就是要偷到蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His goal in life is to steal a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毁掉我们的蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and ruin our restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.85,0:10:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是最可怕的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the worst part of it is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  他没穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good grief, he's naked
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有种就给我穿衣服啊  旱鸭子一群
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clothe me if you can, silly landlubbers
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让你把话收回去  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make you eat those words, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不穿衣服  不穿鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No shirt, no shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不提供服务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no service
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是给我穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过起码是件内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least it's underwire
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,臭汉堡还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your stinking patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我就不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里煤气泄露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there a gas leak in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  蟹黄堡回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knick-knack, the patty's back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成功了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胜利的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory screech
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,享受你胜利的尖叫吧  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your victory screech, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.42,0:11:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有一天  蟹黄堡秘方会到我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because someday the Krabby Patty formula will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对得不到秘方  大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get this formula you twisted fiend
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I will
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我得明天再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even if I have to come back tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.55,0:11:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有再明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the next day
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找你的电话  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phone call, Mr. Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.87,0:11:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:11:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next day
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有再明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the next day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本不值得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不值得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just not worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,心理治疗期间  我会记得你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll remember you all in therapy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全息肉糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holographic meatloaf
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的最爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my favorite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.73,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(357,353)}救生员\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}海绵宝宝
