Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:45.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,734)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.02,0:12:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goo Lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.85,0:12:46.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太阳热着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:46.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where the sun is hot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,日光浴者则
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the sunbathers are
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so cool
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这太阳晒得真舒服阿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you believe that sun?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都能一整天盯着它看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could look at it all day
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.03,0:13:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.76,0:13:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晒得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, how's that tan coming?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me check
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晒得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking good
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你晒得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's yours?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明明记得我是仰面躺着的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could have sworn I was laying on my back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是救生员拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Larry, the lifeguard
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救生员先生  我能摸摸你的肌肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lifeguard, can I feel your muscle?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别刮花了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't scratch the paint
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救生员  海浪行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lifeguard, how's the tubage?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gnarly, dudes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救生员  请问零食吧往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lifeguard, can you point out the snack bar?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right over there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过两位长辈年纪太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you guys are way too old
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来海滩可能不太雅观
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and unsightly for my beach
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕得请你们离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm afraid I'm going to have to ask you to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So polite
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真像是我们养大的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like we raised him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难怪他那么受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it any wonder he's so popular?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.79,0:14:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象一下我是个救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just imagine if I were a lifeguard
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:15.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376,470)}救生员
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样就太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be so cool
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛想当救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want to be a lifeguard for?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没人喜欢他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody really likes those guys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.29,0:14:25.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他是好小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:25.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For he's a jolly, good fellow
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当救生员特别傻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being a lifeguard is so dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只会吹吹吹他们的破哨子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All they do is blow, blow, blow on their stupid whistles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往鼻子涂涂涂那种白色玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,rub, rub, rub that white stuff on their noses
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.90,0:14:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处炫耀他们畸形难看的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and show off their gross misshapen bodies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  把那玩意收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, put that thing away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海滩有小孩子  看不得这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are, like, children here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去零食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the snack bar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁稀罕当什么救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs to be a lifeguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cool
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从头上下都跟拉里一样酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm every bit as cool as Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是不酷  那我就天打
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if I'm not, let me be struck by
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被飞天冰淇淋车砸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A flying ice cream truck
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,砸不死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and live
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.68,0:15:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请勿把飞天冰淇淋车降落到游客身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, do not land
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,flying ice cream trucks on the bathers
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道你是救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were a lifeguard
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lifeguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The nose
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白色玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,White stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是救生员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think I'm a lifeguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.42,0:15:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救生员的气质是藏不住的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's no hiding the lifeguard look, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就有那气质
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真这么觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.82,0:15:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bet, I do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这边人手不太够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, we're a little shorthanded around here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来海滩这边帮忙怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you like to work the beach?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.47,0:15:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等休息了再来抱吧  海滩大汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave that on the bench, Kahuna
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安妮特  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Annette, come here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你见见我兄弟  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to meet my buddy, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.75,0:15:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位是救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guy's a lifeguard
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It works
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚最棒了  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the greatest, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不要等会儿来接我的班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, how'd you like to take the second shift?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By myself?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得准备好了就接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:50.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only if you think you're ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不仅仅准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not just ready
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,730)}氧化锌膏
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还准备好  来哩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Ready Freddie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll just
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有游客落水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got a sinker
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这个让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, let me take this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整天都还没出动救援呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen any action all day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出动救援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Action?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, help
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我呼吸啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breathe, darn you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以后再也不边看书边游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the last time I read and swim
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saved my life
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.19,0:17:49.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:49.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是分内的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the job
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.62,0:17:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然辣妹和大椅子很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the babes and the big chair are great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是最棒的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but the best part is
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以知道只有你才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knowing you're the only thing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让海滩上的游客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that stands between these good people
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃吃吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go, go, go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(676,152)}年度吃热狗大赛
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免于溺亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a watery grave
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是救生员的意义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's what it's all about
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的命现在交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Their lives are in your hands now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去晒日光浴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I got a date with a tanning booth
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.72,0:18:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can't swim
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.00,0:18:23.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道救生员得救生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'd known being a lifeguard
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,meant guarding their lives
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一开始就不会答应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would never have said yes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许不会出岔子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe nothing will go wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后等拉里回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then when Larry comes back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再跟他说我不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him I'm not interested
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何况最惨还能惨到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, what's the worst that could happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体游客上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody out of the water
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of the water
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on, lifeguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the big emergency?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水里有鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are sharks in there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在说我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my family you're talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sea monster
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们海怪极大地促进了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, we sea monsters have made great strides
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科学与文学领域的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the fields of science and literature
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody went?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖大得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a big lagoon, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.03,0:19:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't go
