Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:32.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多得很  大家都有份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plenty for everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份给你  一份给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One for you, one for you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  大家都拿到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody got one?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.09,0:19:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在逮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I got you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们必须得等一小时才能去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, you all have to wait one hour
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before you go swimming
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但为了你们不去冒这个险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But just so you're not tempted
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,912)}禁止跨越
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖封湖了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the lagoon is closed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们更喜欢拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We like Larry better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.43,0:20:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里有没有给过你们免费冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does Larry ever give you free ice cream?
