Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cramp
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy cow
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有游客溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somebody's drowning
