Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If there was anyone in there, we'd hear them
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, help
