Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They would have to have crossed the line
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跨越警戒线才溺水的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm drowning 'cause I crossed the line
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.31,0:21:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take a look
