Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Butt hurts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, help
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.92,0:21:20.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:20.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't move
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Catch this
