Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit fooling around, man
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.75,0:21:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in the water
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, help
