Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.78,0:21:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.52,0:21:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.87,0:21:35.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得跑起来想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:35.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to run around and think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得边跑起来边想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to run around and think at the same time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.76,0:21:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得想想  得有计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to think, got to have a plan
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得想想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to think, think, think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.77,0:21:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星没水就不会溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick can't drown if there isn't any water
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.03,0:21:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你安全了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're safe now, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  我溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, I'm drowning
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我屁股抽筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got butt cramps
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.20,0:21:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要冰淇淋  现在天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want ice cream and now it's dark
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命啊  我溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help me, I'm drowning
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.80,0:22:08.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:08.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.77,0:22:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敬我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To us
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.65,0:22:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.27,0:22:14.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗还你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:14.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.18,0:22:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了派大星  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.03,0:22:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, come 'round Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.17,0:22:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I am
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.90,0:22:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, Pat, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.17,0:22:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it, hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.90,0:22:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, Pat, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.65,0:22:23.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  派大星住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:23.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Pat, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.78,0:22:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.32,0:22:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.99,0:22:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
