Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save me, can't swim
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.55,0:22:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.74,0:22:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.77,0:22:39.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:39.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.18,0:22:43.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:43.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help us
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.34,0:22:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're drowning
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.09,0:22:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道电影院现在在放什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's showing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at the movie theater right about now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.55,0:22:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.55,0:22:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  冰淇淋
