Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.50,0:22:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  不会游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, can't swim
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.57,0:23:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.64,0:23:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Larry?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.87,0:23:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该不是救生员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.87,0:23:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not a lifeguard, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.90,0:23:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.87,0:23:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.87,0:23:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.02,0:23:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.32,0:23:11.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们学得挺快的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:11.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fellows are learning fast
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁股抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.68,0:23:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Butt cramps
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.47,0:23:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是没有冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.47,0:23:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I still don't have my ice cream
